Package: inv4mhighland
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Analysis of Inv4m Chromosomal Inversion Effects in Highland Maize
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fausto", "Rodriguez", email = "fvrodriguez@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Highland Maize Research Team", role = "aut")
)
Description: Comprehensive spatial analysis tools for studying the effects of the Inv4m 
    chromosomal inversion in maize varieties adapted to Mexican highlands. Provides 
    functions for multi-omics spatial field experiments including RNA-seq, lipidomics, 
    and ionomics data analysis with proper spatial correlation modeling.
